articles.title: Taylor Swift And Joe Alwyn Break Up After Six Years Of Dating - NDTV
articles.description: American singer Taylor Swift and British actor Joe Alwyn parted ways a few weeks ago and the split was amicable.
articles.content:
American singer Taylor Swift and British actor Joe Alwyn.
American singer Taylor Swift and British actor Joe Alwyn have broken up after dating for a period of six years, as per a report in Page Six.… [+2110 chars]
